spec_data.Name: glibc-nss-devel
spec_data.License: LGPLv2+ and LGPLv2+ with exceptions and GPLv2+
spec_data.Description:
The glibc-nss-devel package contains the object files necessary to
compile applications and libraries which directly link against NSS
modules supplied by glibc.

This is a rare and special use case; regular development has to use
the glibc-devel package instead.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 02 Nov 2017 07:30:20 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Development files for directly linking NSS service modules
